#month-banner("Three", "Eight", "The Living Laboratory: Long-Term Practice", "The laboratory as continuous presence — Inhabiting the Work across time")

#v(0.8em)

#hm-note[
  Month 8 is the most practical and structural month of Year Three's inner arc.
  It does not introduce new concepts — it consolidates what has been built and
  turns the practitioner's attention toward what lies ahead beyond the curriculum.
  The post-curriculum practice declaration is the most significant deliverable:
  it tests whether the student has genuinely internalised the Work or is merely
  completing an educational programme. A student who cannot articulate a
  meaningful post-curriculum practice has not yet made the Work their own.
]

